r Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When William Berenger II was born in 1463, in Wiltshire, England, his father, William Berenger I, was 21 and his mother, Katherine Luster, was 21. He had at least 1 daughter with Elizabeth Fettiplace. He died in 1493, in Manningford Bruce, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 30, and was buried in Aldbourne, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1463–1493":"1463–1493","1465–1534":"1465–1534","1462–1489":"1462–1489","1489–1534":"1489–1534","1442–1483":"1442–1483","1442–1492":"1442–1492","1534":"1534","1489":"1489","1465":"1465","1442":"1442","1463":"1463","1462":"1462","1483":"1483","1493":"1493","1492":"1492","Wiltshire, England":"Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Manningford Bruce, Berkshire, England":"Manningford Bruce, Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Manningford Bruce, Wiltshire, England":"Manningford Bruce, Wiltshire, England","Aldbourne, Wiltshire, England":"Aldbourne, Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1463–1493":"1463–1493","1465–1534":"1465–1534","1462–1489":"1462–1489","1489–1534":"1489–1534","1442–1483":"1442–1483","1442–1492":"1442–1492","1534":"1534","1489":"1489","1465":"1465","1442":"1442","1463":"1463","1462":"1462","1483":"1483","1493":"1493","1492":"1492","Wiltshire, England":"Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Manningford Bruce, Berkshire, England":"Manningford Bruce, Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Manningford Bruce, Wiltshire, England":"Manningford Bruce, Wiltshire, England","Aldbourne, Wiltshire, England":"Aldbourne, Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1463–1493":"1463–1493","1465–1534":"1465–1534","1462–1489":"1462–1489","1489–1534":"1489–1534","1442–1483":"1442–1483","1442–1492":"1442–1492","1534":"1534","1489":"1489","1465":"1465","1442":"1442","1463":"1463","1462":"1462","